'''Manḍhâlika''' (''Gloriosa superba'') iyâ arèya totombuwân sè tamaso' ka ḍâlem famili Colchicaceae. Totombuwân arèya èkoca' kèya ''flame lily'', ''superb lily'' (Inggris); ''kembang sungsang'' (Inḍonesia); ''pacing tawa'' (Jhâbâ); ''katongkat'' (Sonḍhâ) bân èn-laènna<ref>https://uses.plantnet-project.org/en/Gloriosa_superba_(PROSEA)</ref>.
